tica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2012/T5/anmu%2036.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n', 'Chuyện ít biết về cuộc hội ngộ kỳ lạ dưới bóng cây Thiên Quang Ni Tự', 0);
INSERT INTO `chuathienquang_news` (`id`, `id_category`, `author`, `date`, `content`, `title`, `type`) VALUES
(42, 10, 'Diệu Bảo', '2013-01-21 08:36:30', '<div class="img_caption left" style="font-size: 12px; text-align: center !important; float: left; margin-right: 1em; margin-top: 3px; width: 241px;"><img align="left" border="0" class="caption" height="161" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%201.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(216, 216, 216); text-align: center !important; padding: 3px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" width="241" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ng&agrave;y 21-9, sau gần 6 th&aacute;ng thi c&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n tục, c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh t&acirc;n tạo tam quan v&agrave; tường hoa Thi&ecirc;n Quang Ni Tự theo phong c&aacute;ch kiến tr&uacute;c truyền thống Phật gi&aacute;o miền Bắc, do sư c&ocirc; Th&iacute;ch nữ Hương Nhũ l&agrave;m trụ tr&igrave;, đ&atilde; ho&agrave;n h&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n m&atilde;n tốt đẹp, g&oacute;p phần t&ocirc; điểm v&agrave;o vườn hoa Phật gi&aacute;o B&igrave;nh Dương th&ecirc;m sắc ng&aacute;t hương.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial,Tahoma,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Với chủ &yacute; đề cao văn h&oacute;a d&acirc;n tộc v&agrave; xiển dương ch&acirc;n l&yacute; Phật-đ&agrave;, tam quan (cao 12,5 m&eacute;t, ngang 16 m&eacute;t, s&acirc;u 4 m&eacute;t) v&agrave; tường hoa (cao 2,9 m&eacute;t, d&agrave;i 416 m&eacute;t) của Thi&ecirc;n Quang Ni Tự được x&acirc;y dựng tr&ecirc;n khu đất diện t&iacute;ch hơn 01 h&eacute;c-ta tọa lạc tại ấp T&acirc;n H&ograve;a, phường Đ&ocirc;ng H&ograve;a, thị x&atilde; Dĩ An, tỉnh B&igrave;nh Dương.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial,Tahoma,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Ch&ugrave;a Thi&ecirc;n Quang do ni trưởng Th&iacute;ch Nữ Huệ Gi&aacute;c, viện chủ Quan &Acirc;m Tu Viện &ndash; TP. Bi&ecirc;n H&ograve;a&nbsp; khai sơn năm 1972 dưới sự chứng minh của cố H&ograve;a thượng Th&iacute;ch Thiện Phước, sơ Tổ s&aacute;ng lập Li&ecirc;n t&ocirc;ng Tịnh độ Non Bồng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial,Tahoma,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Ng&agrave;y 4/12/2010, ni trưởng Huệ Gi&aacute;c k&yacute; Giấy Giao ph&oacute;, giao cho đệ tử l&agrave; sư c&ocirc; Hương Nhũ tr&aacute;ch nhiệm quản l&yacute;, điều h&agrave;nh phật sự v&agrave; x&acirc;y dựng Thi&ecirc;n Quang Ni Tự trở th&agrave;nh một trung t&acirc;m tu học cho chư ni v&agrave; Phật tử, nhất l&agrave; giới trẻ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%201.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%203.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%204.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%205.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%202.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%2025.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">蓮 花 最 勝 徵 妙 法</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Li&ecirc;n Hoa tối thắng trưng Diệu Ph&aacute;p</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">宗 德 上 乘 闡 大 悲</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T&ocirc;ng Đức thượng thừa xiển Đại Bi</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%206.jpg" style="border: none;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">天 界 有 重.望 彌 勒 聖 宮 眾 蒼 生 恆 瞻 兜率</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Thi&ecirc;n giới hữu tr&ugrave;ng, vọng Di-Lặc th&aacute;nh cung ch&uacute;ng thương sinh hằng chi&ecirc;m Đ&acirc;u Suất</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">光 輝 無 量.向 彌 陀 淨 土 兹 派 徒 奉 獻 蓬 瀛</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Quang huy v&ocirc; lượng, hướng Di-Đ&agrave; &nbsp;Tịnh Độ tư &nbsp;ph&aacute;i đồ phụng hiến Bồng Doanh (hoặc Dinh)</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>Tạm dịch:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>Thi&ecirc;n giới vạn tr&ugrave;ng, ngưỡng Di Lặc th&aacute;nh cung, bao sinh linh hằng mong Đ&acirc;u Suất.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>Phật quang v&ocirc; lượng, hướng Di Đ&agrave; Tịnh Độ, ch&uacute;ng ph&aacute;i đồ phụng hiến Bồng Dinh</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%2012.jpg" style="border: none;" /></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%2013.jpg" style="border: none;" /></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%207.jpg" style="border: none;" /></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">福 慧 雙 修.善 解 真 心 悉 會 於 覺 境</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Phước Huệ song tu, thiện giải ch&acirc;n t&acirc;m tất hội ư gi&aacute;c cảnh</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">淨 禪 一 理.信 知 正 道 同 歸 而 殊 途</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Tịnh Thiền nhất l&yacute;, t&iacute;n tri ch&iacute;nh đạo đồng quy &nbsp;nhi th&ugrave; đồ</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>Tạm dịch:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>Ph&uacute;c huệ song tu , thấy&nbsp; r&otilde;&nbsp; ch&acirc;n&nbsp; t&acirc;m&nbsp; tất&nbsp; thảy&nbsp; về &nbsp;c&otilde;i&nbsp; gi&aacute;c .</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>Tịnh thiền nhất l&yacute;, hiểu ra ch&aacute;nh đạo c&ugrave;ng đ&iacute;ch tuy kh&aacute;c đường.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%208.jpg" style="border: none;" /></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">般 若 真 空.觀 四 時 行 然 如 夢 如 幻</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">B&aacute;t nh&atilde; ch&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng, qu&aacute;n tứ thời h&agrave;nh nhi&ecirc;n như mộng như huyễn</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">華 嚴 妙 有.任 萬 物 生 化 不 即 不 離</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hoa Nghi&ecirc;m diệu hữu, nhậm vạn vật sinh h&oacute;a bất tức&nbsp; &nbsp;bất&nbsp;&nbsp; ly</p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>Tạm dịch:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>B&aacute;t Nh&atilde; ch&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng, xem bốn m&ugrave;a vần xoay như mộng như ảo.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em>Hoa Nghi&ecirc;m diệu hữu, mặc vạn vật sinh h&oacute;a kh&ocirc;ng vướng kh&ocirc;ng l&igrave;a</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p align="center" style="margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em><img border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2011/T9/0004thienquang%209.jpg" style="border: none;" /></em></